  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6417537">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6417537/" class="title-link">太平洋的对岸会有如此惬意的生活</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6417537"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/80169163/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/80169163/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">sysjc</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-11-19"
      class="main-meta">2013-11-19 10:37:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6417537_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看得出三联与林达夫妇的友好密切关系，在各种式样版本的林达作品不断出版后，今年又推出了作品合集，这是旁人无法比拟的待遇，虽说当然有作品销路不成问题的原因，但我更愿看成是三联借作品而行的一次“洗脑”。  林达的作品脉络分明，条理清晰，而且饶有趣味，大部分读起来轻...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6417537/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">13有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6417537_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6417537_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8535301">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8535301/" class="title-link">梦想照进现实</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8535301"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/152607965/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u152607965-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/152607965/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Sunny 🌹</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-05-12"
      class="main-meta">2017-05-12 15:07:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8535301_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是今年读来的第一套书，其实是先入了几本，后来被惊艳到了，就陆续买齐，基本以每周两本的速度在读。      这套书应该是绝佳的美国历史、人文政治的入门书籍，读完这套书基本可以了解美国社会的根本制度，历史及社会的整体框架。无疑美国的强大举世共睹，存在自有他的合理性...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
